WEBVTT

00:00.020 --> 00:00.900
Come on, smile.

00:02.800 --> 00:03.630
Pittsburgh police.

00:03.730 --> 00:04.970
You're under arrest for murder.

00:06.670 --> 00:07.240
She's innocent.

00:07.400 --> 00:08.700
Laura is not getting out.

00:09.680 --> 00:10.440
What do you wanna know?

00:10.580 --> 00:12.940
How you escaped from jail when no one else could.

00:13.920 --> 00:16.320
You have to have the entire plan already in place.

00:16.700 --> 00:18.150
No prison in the world is airtight.

00:19.640 --> 00:20.580
Do not do this.

00:21.550 --> 00:22.600
We have no other choice.

00:24.450 --> 00:25.820
The Next Three Days.

00:27.530 --> 00:30.120
Rated PG-13. In theaters everywhere, November 19th.

